<wxs module="util" src="../../utils/util.wxs" />
<view class='logo'>
  <image src="{{util.HTTP}}mobile/small/image/login.png" class="icon-wx"></image>
  <image src="{{configSwitch.appInfo.logo}}" class="icon-logo"></image>
</view>
<view class='content-bg'>
  <image src='{{util.HTTP}}mobile/small/image/sj.png'></image>
  <text>+86</text>
  <input placeholder='请输入手机号' maxlength='11' type='number' bindinput='phoneInput' value='{{phone}}'></input>
</view>
<view class='content-bg'>
  <image src='{{util.HTTP}}mobile/small/image/mm.png'></image>
  <input placeholder='请输入6-20位密码' maxlength='20' type='text' password value='{{password}}' bindinput='pswInput'></input>
</view>
<view class='tips'>
  您填写手机号码和密码用于补全您的{{configSwitch.appInfo.title}}账号信息。补全后,手机号或微信账号均可登录{{configSwitch.appInfo.title}}商城。
</view>
<view class='content-bg submit' hover-class='hover-class' hover-stay-time='400' bindtap='submit' style='{{util.diyColor("",diyColor.zColor,"")}}'>
  关联
</view>
<view class='tips'>
  若您输入的手机号未注册,将为您直接注册,注册即视为同意
  <text hover-class='hover-class' hover-stay-time='400' bindtap='onWeb' style='{{util.diyColor(diyColor.zColor,"","")}}'>
    《注册协议》
  </text>
</view>